### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Récupérer l'historique complet (cas nominal)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments-get-payment-history
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 2 - Filtrer par événement
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments-get-payment-history?event_id=event-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 3 - Filtrer par statut
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments-get-payment-history?status=paid
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 4 - Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments-get-payment-history?page=2&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test 5 - Combinaison de filtres
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments-get-payment-history?event_id=event-uuid-here&status=pending&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

